data.description: Sweet ranch positioned on a quiet street. Open floor plan with an updated kitchen boasting granite countertop, Corian counters, convection oven, tile backsplash & refinished cabinets! All new Pergo wood flooring on main floor. New paint throughout. New tuff shed and gazebo in backyard. New French doors in dining room. Master offers designer tile, handcrafted wood cabinet, multi function spray head & glassed in shower. 3 bedrooms, 2 baths with a partially finished basement offering a new 3/4 bath, coffee bar & added hallway with endless closets. Fully landscaped! Walk to lake & park!
